graph LR
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller<br/>Kubeflow Component]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    NotebookController -->|CRUD operations<br/>HTTPS/443| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API 1.22+<br/>Required]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| StatefulSet[StatefulSet API<br/>apps/v1<br/>Required]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| ServiceAPI[Service API<br/>v1<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    NotebookController -->|VirtualServices<br/>when USE_ISTIO=true| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>networking.istio.io/v1alpha3<br/>Optional]
    NotebookController -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|created by| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI/API]
    NotebookController -.->|multi-tenancy<br/>Kubeflow mode| Profiles[Kubeflow Profiles<br/>CRD]
    NotebookController -->|references| NotebookImages[Notebook Images<br/>Container Registry]
    NotebookController -.->|optional sidecar| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift Auth]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages<br/>Notebook CRs| NotebookController
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|may trigger<br/>notebook creation| NotebookController

    %% External Services
    NotebookController -->|image pulls| Registry[Container Registry<br/>External]
    NotebookController -->|query activity<br/>HTTP/80| NotebookServices[Notebook Services<br/>Created Resources]

    %% Variant-specific
    subgraph Variants["Deployment Variants"]
        KF[Kubeflow Variant<br/>- USE_ISTIO=true<br/>- KFAM integration]
        ODH[ODH/OpenShift Variant<br/>- USE_ISTIO=false<br/>- ADD_FSGROUP=false<br/>- Konflux builds]
    end

    NotebookController -.->|deployed as| Variants

